      "@type": "Dataset",
      "name": "SSc-MIM: Molecular Interaction Map of Skin Fibrosis in Diffuse Cutaneous Systemic Sclerosis",
      "description": "First curated, SBGN-Process-Description-compliant Molecular Interaction Map of dcSSc skin fibrosis. 526 species, 260 reactions, 17 biologically meaningful compartments. MI2CAST-annotated; overlaid with 4 open-access single-cell transcriptomic datasets (Tabib 2021 / Gur 2022 / GSE128169 / GSE210395; 197 donors, 266 884 cells, 58 cell-type clusters). Built in CellDesigner; pipeline orchestrated via a GNU Makefile and a scanpy + statsmodels + NetworkX Python stack.",
